{"tid":668042,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★LogiTech Crayon手寫筆已開售：蘋果iPad專用，不支持壓感","createTime":"2018-05-17T09:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T13:19:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9604c4c39b8c27d6d120d28c4a85fc3f3eb51eab","tid":668042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"在3月27日的教育研討會上，蘋果發布了一台9.7英寸的iPad，那麼是不是除此之外就沒有其他新品了呢？其實當天蘋果還和羅技合作推出了一款&ldquo;蠟筆&rdquo;Crayon，這款入門級手寫筆終於在今天上線銷售了，定價49.95美元，只對教育人員開放購買，至於國內暫時還沒有上線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/5/20180517110231_6804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F5%2F20180517110231_6804.jpg&h=1eb160cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple Pencil作為蘋果官方推出的手寫筆，售價高達100美元，這對於不少學生來說可能有些太貴了，所以為了搭配售價329美元的新iPad，蘋果聯合羅技推出了Crayon。當時蘋果承諾這只手寫筆將會在夏季上市，現在他們兌現了承諾。<br />\n<br />\n羅技強調，Crayon採用了Apple Pencil中的技術，能夠提供亞像素級別的精度、低延遲體驗，並且還能夠感應到筆身的傾斜，非常適合學生使用。iPad也採用了手掌識別技術，當手放在螢幕上時，能夠區分手部和羅技Crayon手寫筆，防止手掌影響手寫筆的活動。<br />\n<br />\n但是最為關鍵的一點是，羅技Crayon不支持Apple Pencil的壓感體驗，粗大的筆尖使其更擅長繪製粗線條。同時羅技Crayon使用的充電介面為Lightning母口，所以不能像Apple Pencil那樣插到iPad Pro上充電，而是需要接上電纜，一次充電能夠支持8小時的使用。<br />\n<br />\n並且羅技Crayon只支持今年發布的第六代iPad，包括iPad Pro在內的設備並不支持它，因為它的信號傳輸依靠的是短程射頻，而不是Apple Pencil使用的藍牙。不過外媒猜測，未來推出的iPad Pro將會內置短頻接收器以支持羅技Crayon這樣的設備，並且未來也會有越來越多第三方手寫筆誕生。<br />\n<br />\n總的來說，這是一款專門為學生，甚至是低齡學生準備的手寫筆，並且只在蘋果教育商店開放購買，所以如果你想要的是一支強大的手寫筆，請購買Apple Pencil。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/ipad/360187.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fipad%2F360187.htm&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6f0afe3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/ipad/360187.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f2c4360058e802b7756173cde34ec540c81c3e6","tid":668042,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"羅技Crayon不支持Apple Pencil的壓感體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ff3caea46626ce119ed00ed8863b40942e86d2","tid":668042,"uid":35233,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:13:22.000Z","msg":"依種叉電方式好過APPLE PENCIL 好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac8cf04099d52b08b6bdce508fc49159230f31c","tid":668042,"uid":49693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2c4360058e802b7756173cde34ec540c81c3e6","tid":668042,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"羅技Crayon不支持Apple Pencil的壓感體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"但又自稱用咗apple pencil個技術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0899ce6b5b33f62b776a8bc264adcd5c22490f05","tid":668042,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a84cd44e7ffd5d743e7cc18eef4c98d8171f41d","tid":668042,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:36:53.000Z","